  "root_cause": "Rust raw-string regex literals in two callgraph helpers used double-escaped \\s/\\w (e.g. r\"^\\\\s*export...\"). The compiled regex saw a literal backslash-s rather than a whitespace class, so find_js_ts_default_export_name, parse_java_like_package, and parse_csharp_namespace silently returned None on every realistic input.",
